<plot>The first documentary film to unite Arab and Israeli skaters for a lighter take on Politics in the Middle East. SOUR presents an action packed look at the grassroots peace process begun in 2006 during the Second Lebanese Conflict. Filmed on location in Jordan and Israel by the teenage skaters involved in the film in essence, SOUR is a film about doing what you love with people you're not supposed to like.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?508275</url></doc>
